{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/swift-MVVM/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"swift-mvvm패턴\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#swift-mvvm%ED%8C%A8%ED%84%B4\" aria-label=\"swift mvvm패턴 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Swift MVVM패턴</h3>\n<p>드디어 ios 개발에서 디자인 패턴을 적용해 개발하기 시작했다.</p>\n<p>MVVM 패턴이 가장 벨런스가 잘 잡혀있고 많이 사용되는 디자인 패턴이기 때문에 채택했다.</p>\n<p>MVVM 패턴은 M(Model), V(View), VM(ViewModel)로 이루어진 패턴이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 585px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1519f223c0451018f8aa1b9c6261f347/78a22/mvvm.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.891891891891895%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mvvm\"\n        title=\"mvvm\"\n        src=\"/static/1519f223c0451018f8aa1b9c6261f347/78a22/mvvm.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1519f223c0451018f8aa1b9c6261f347/12f09/mvvm.png 148w,\n/static/1519f223c0451018f8aa1b9c6261f347/e4a3f/mvvm.png 295w,\n/static/1519f223c0451018f8aa1b9c6261f347/78a22/mvvm.png 585w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>바로 예제를 통해 각 블럭이 어떤 역할을 하는지 알아보자.</p>\n<h3 id=\"model\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#model\" aria-label=\"model permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Model</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Model</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">String</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Int</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> image<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">UIImage</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">UIImage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>named<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token delimiter variable\">\\(</span>name<span class=\"token delimiter variable\">)</span></span>.jpg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> name\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bounty <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> bounty\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이름, 현상금, 이미지에 대한 변수를 가지는 모델이다.</p>\n<p>model은 보통 한 화면에 여러개 생성되는 블럭, 구조를 뜻하며 코드로는 struct로 생성되며 변수와 생성자가 포함된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"viewmodel\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#viewmodel\" aria-label=\"viewmodel permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ViewModel</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BountyViewModel</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> bountyInfoList<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token builtin\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"brook\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">33000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"chopper\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"franky\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">44000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"luffy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">300000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"nami\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">16000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"robin\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">80000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"sanji\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">77000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"zoro\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bounty<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">12000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> sortedList<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token builtin\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> sortedList <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> bountyInfoList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">sorted</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> prev<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> next <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> prev<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bounty <span class=\"token operator\">></span> next<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bounty\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> sortedList\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> numOfBountyInfoList<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> bountyInfoList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">count</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function\">bountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>at index<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">BountyInfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> sortedList<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>index<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>ViewModel에서는 만들어둔 모델을 다룬다.</p>\n<p>위에서 만들어둔 BountyInfo를 선언해 배열을 만들고 그 배열에 관한 정보를 리턴해주는 함수를 포함하고 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"view\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#view\" aria-label=\"view permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>View</h3>\n<p>view는 말 그래도 화면에 띄워주는 부분이다.</p>\n<p>StoryBoard로 개발시 ViewController가 view역할을 하게 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> viewModel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">BountyViewModel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위 그림을 보면 알 수 있듯이 view는 viewModel과 연결되어있다.</p>\n<p>따라서 ViewController에서 viewModel을 받아 사용해주면 된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"참고해야할-점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC%ED%95%A0-%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"참고해야할 점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고해야할 점</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>그림에서와 같이 view와 model은 절대 직접적으로 연결되어선 안된다.</li>\n<li>함수는 한 가지 일만 해야한다.</li>\n<li>함수는 20줄을 넘기지 말고, 클래스는 100줄을 넘기지 말자 (최대한)</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p>디자인 패턴을 적용해 개발을 해보니 이게 내가 원하는 패턴이 맞는건가? 하는 생각이 자주 들었다.</p>\n<p>구조가 조금 잘못된다 하더라도 에러가 뜨지도 않고 아무리 구조를 잘 짰다 하더라도 그게 맞는건지 알 수 없었다.</p>\n<p>최대한 잘 짠 코드를 많이 보며 패턴을 눈에 익히는 것만이 방법인 것 같다...</p>","excerpt":"Swift MVVM패턴 드디어 ios 개발에서 디자인 패턴을 적용해 개발하기 시작했다. MVVM 패턴이 가장 벨런스가 잘 잡혀있고 많이 사용되는 디자인 패턴이기 때문에 채택했다. MVVM 패턴은 M(Model), V(View), VM(ViewMode…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/swift-MVVM/#swift-mvvm%ED%8C%A8%ED%84%B4\">Swift MVVM패턴</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/swift-MVVM/#model\">Model</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/swift-MVVM/#viewmodel\">ViewModel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/swift-MVVM/#view\">View</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/swift-MVVM/#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC%ED%95%A0-%EC%A0%90\">참고해야할 점</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/swift-MVVM/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Swift MVVM","date":"Jun 22, 2021","tags":["Swift"],"keywords":["MojitoBar","Ju dongseok"],"update":"Jun 22, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/swift-MVVM/","series":[],"lastmod":"2021-06-22"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}